tration%20in%20Sector%2026%20for%20the%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20also%20joined%20the%20meeting%2C%20which%20began%20at%208.15%20pm%20on%20Sunday%20and%20ended%20at%20around%201%20am%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20reporters%20after%20the%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Goyal%20said%20the%20panel%20has%20proposed%20the%20buying%20of%20pulses%2C%20maize%2C%20and%20cotton%20crops%20by%20government%20agencies%20at%20minimum%20support%20prices%20for%20five%20years%20after%20entering%20into%20an%20agreement%20with%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmer%20leaders%20said%20they%20will%20discuss%20the%20government's%20proposal%20in%20their%20forums%20over%20the%20next%20two%20days%20and%20thereafter%2C%20decide%20the%20future%20course%20of%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCooperative%20societies%20like%20the%20NCCF%20(National%20Cooperative%20Consumers%20Federation)%20and%20NAFED%20(National%20Agricultural%20Cooperative%20Marketing%20Federation%20of%20India)%20will%20enter%20into%20a%20contract%20with%20those%20farmers%20who%20grow%20'tur%20dal'%2C%20'urad%20dal'%2C%20'masoor%20dal'%20or%20maize%20for%20buying%20their%20crop%20at%20MSP%20for%20next%20five%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Goyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20no%20limit%20on%20the%20quantity%20(purchased)%20and%20a%20portal%20will%20be%20developed%20for%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20save%20Punjab's%20farming%2C%20improve%20the%20groundwater%20table%2C%20and%20save%20the%20land%20from%20getting%20barren%20which%20is%20already%20under%20stress%2C%20Mr%20Goyal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Centre's%20proposal%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20discuss%20in%20our%20forums%20on%20February%2019-20%20and%20take%20the%20opinion%20of%20experts%20regarding%20it%20and%20accordingly%20take%20a%20decision.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20discussion%20on%20loan%20waivers%20and%20other%20demands%20is%20pending%20and%20we%20hope%20that%20these%20will%20be%20resolved%20in%20the%20next%20two%20days%2C%20Mr%20Pandher%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20'Delhi%20Chalo'%20march%20is%20currently%20on%20hold%2C%20but%20will%20resume%20at%2011%20am%20on%20February%2021%20if%20all%20the%20issues%20are%20not%20resolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20ministers%20and%20farmer%20leaders%20had%20met%20earlier%20on%20February%208%2C%2012%20and%2015%20but%20the%20talks%20remained%20inconclusive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtesting%20farmers%20from%20Punjab%20have%20been%20camping%20at%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri%20points%20on%20the%20state's%20border%20with%20Haryana%20since%20February%2013%20when%20their%20'Delhi%20Chalo'%20march%20was%20halted%20by%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20call%20for%20the%20march%20was%20given%20by%20the%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(Non-Political)%20and%20the%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20to%20press%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20of%20MSP%2C%20the%20farmers%20are%20demanding%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission's%20recommendations%2C%20pension%20for%20farmers%20and%20farm%20labourers%2C%20farm%20debt%20waiver%2C%20no%20hike%20in%20electricity%20tariff%2C%20withdrawal%20of%20police%20cases%20and%20%26quot%3Bjustice%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20victims%20of%20the%202021%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20violence%2C%20reinstatement%20of%20the%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act%2C%202013%2C%20and%20compensation%20to%20the%20families%20of%20the%20farmers%20who%20died%20during%20a%20previous%20agitation%20in%202020-21.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20fourth%20round%20of%20talks%2C%20the%20SKM%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20gherao%20the%20residences%20of%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20Punjab%20for%20three%20days%20from%20Tuesday%20to%20press%20the%20Centre%20into%20accepting%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalbir%20Singh%20Rajewal%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20SKM%2C%20an%20umbrella%20body%20of%20various%20farmer%20unions%2C%20said%20they%20will%20stage%20protests%20in%20front%20of%20the%20residences%20of%20Punjab%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20including%20MPs%2C%20MLAs%20and%20district%20presidents%2C%20from%20Tuesday%20to%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInteracting%20with%20reporters%20after%20a%20meeting%20of%20SKM%20leaders%20in%20Ludhiana%2C%20Mr%20Rajewal%20said%20it%20has%20also%20been%20decided%20that%20they%20would%20protest%20at%20all%20toll%20barriers%20in%20the%20state%20and%20make%20them%20free%20for%20all%20commuters%20from%20February%2020%20to%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SKM%20will%20not%20accept%20anything%20less%20than%20the%20C-2%20plus%2050%20per%20cent%20formula%20for%20MSP%20as%20recommended%20in%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission%20report%2C%20he%20said%20after%20the%20meeting%20which%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20farmer%20leaders%20Balkaran%20Singh%20Brar%20and%20Boota%20Singh%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%20said%20the%20central%20government%20should%20not%20dilly-dally%20and%20accept%20farmers'%20demands%20before%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20comes%20into%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20government%20thinks%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20hold%20meetings%20till%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20is%20imposed%20and%20then%20say%20it%20cannot%20do%20anything%20as%20the%20code%20is%20in%20force...%20the%20farmers%20are%20not%20going%20to%20return%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20should%20find%20a%20solution%20to%20our%20demands%20before%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20comes%20into%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Haryana's%20Kurukshetra%2C%20Bharatiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(Charuni)%20chief%20Gurnam%20Singh%20Charuni%20and%20some%20'khaps'%20took%20part%20in%20a%20panchayat%20to%20chalk%20out%20a%20course%20of%20action%20to%20support%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20from%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Charuni%20told%20reporters%20after%20the%20meeting%20that%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20unite%20all%20farmer%20organisations%20to%20hold%20a%20protest%20in%20support%20of%20the%20agitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Charuni%20said%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20the%20rural%20belt%20is%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%20and%20a%20four-member%20committee%20has%20been%20formed%20to%20connect%20with%20farmers%20from%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20is%20surprising%20that%20the%20government%20is%20not%20allowing%20the%20farmers%20to%20travel%20to%20Delhi%20on%20their%20tractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhap%20leader%20O%20P%20Dhankar%20said%20Haryana%20'khaps'%20are%20behind%20the%20agitation%20and%20the%20central%20government%20should%20not%20delay%20giving%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20of%20MSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20'khap'%20leader%20who%20attended%20the%20panchayat%20said%20farmers%20will%20reach%20Delhi%20and%20protest%20if%20the%20talks%20fail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20suspension%20of%20internet%20services%20has%20been%20extended%20in%20certain%20areas%20in%20some%20Punjab%20districts%2C%20including%20Patiala%2C%20Sangrur%20and%20Fatehgarh%20Sahib%2C%20till%20February%2024%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20internet%20services%20were%20suspended%20from%20February%2012%20to%2016%20in%20view%20of%20the%20farmers'%20march.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharti%20Kisan%20Union%20(Ekta%20Ugrahan)%20continued%20to%20hold%20protests%20at%20toll%20plazas%20in%20Punjab%20for%20the%20second%20consecutive%20day%2C%20forcing%20authorities%20not%20to%20charge%20toll%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Ladhowal%20plaza%20in%20Ludhiana%2C%20farmers%20shouted%20slogans%20against%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20Haryana%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20government%20on%20Saturday%20extended%20the%20ban%20on%20mobile%20internet%20and%20bulk%20SMS%20services%20in%20seven%20districts%20till%20February%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708297260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F2j98gc38_farmers_625x300_19_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmer-leaders-meeting-piyush-goyal-proposal-msp-crops-underground-water-inform-tomorrow-5083673%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20panel%20of%20Union%20ministers%20held%20a%20fourth%20round%20of%20talks%20with%20farmer%20leaders%20here%20on%20Sunday%20over%20their%20demands%2C%20including%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20of%20MSP%2C%20as%20thousands%20of%20protesting%20farmers%20camped%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20border.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmer-leaders-meeting-piyush-goyal-proposal-msp-crops-underground-water-inform-tomorrow-5083673%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmer-leaders-meeting-piyush-goyal-proposal-msp-crops-underground-water-inform-tomorrow-5083673%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffarmer-leaders-meeting-piyush-goyal-proposal-msp-crops-underground-water-inform-tomorrow-5083673%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MSP%20guarantee%20only%20way%20to%20curb%20'cheating'%20by%20traders%3A%20SKM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708297207000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107804459%2Cimgsize-1822979.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fmsp-guarantee-only-way-to-curb-cheating-by-traders-skm%2Farticleshow%2F107804457.cms%22%2C%22summa