l%20Body's%20'Real%20NCP'%20Order%20In%20Court%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20scheduled%20to%20hear%20on%20Monday%20a%20plea%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%20challenging%20an%20Election%20Commission%20order%20recognising%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20faction%20as%20the%20real%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Surya%20Kant%2C%20Dipankar%20Datta%20and%20KV%20Viswanathan%20is%20likely%20to%20hear%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2016%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20agreed%20to%20urgently%20list%20the%20plea%20after%20Sharad%20Pawar%20stated%20that%20a%20whip%20may%20be%20issued%20by%20the%20faction%20led%20by%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20leader%20had%20sought%20an%20urgent%20hearing%20of%20his%20plea%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20twin%20blows%20suffered%20by%20the%20group%20led%20by%20him%20and%20the%20consequential%20fear%20of%20facing%20action%20for%20possible%20violations%20of%20whip%20by%20his%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharad%20Pawar%20had%20sought%20urgent%20hearing%20in%20view%20of%20the%20February%2015%20order%20of%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20Speaker%20Rahul%20Narwekar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Narwekar%20held%20that%20the%20NCP%20faction%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar%20was%20the%20real%20NCP%20and%20that%20the%20anti-defection%20provisions%20in%20the%20Constitution%20cannot%20be%20used%20to%20stifle%20internal%20dissent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20this%2C%20the%20poll%20panel%20announced%20on%20February%206%20that%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20is%20the%20real%20NCP%20and%20also%20allotted%20the%20party's%20'clock'%20symbol%20to%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20special%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20session%20is%20beginning%20on%20February%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawar%20senior%2C%20who%20founded%20the%20NCP%20with%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20speaker%20Purno%20Sangma%20and%20Tariq%20Anwar%20in%201999%20after%20their%20expulsion%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20filed%20the%20petition%20through%20lawyer%20Abhishek%20Jebaraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20him%2C%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20had%20filed%20a%20caveat%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20through%20advocate%20Abhikalp%20Pratap%20Singh%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20ex-parte%20order%20is%20passed%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20group%20if%20the%20latter%20moves%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar%2C%20currently%20a%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20had%20walked%20away%20with%20a%20majority%20of%20NCP%20MLAs%20in%20July%20last%20year%20and%20supported%20the%20BJP-Shiv%20Sena%20government%20led%20by%20Eknath%20Shinde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...this%20commission%20holds%20that%20the%20faction%20led%20by%20the%20petitioner%2C%20Sh%20Ajit%20Anantrao%20Pawar%2C%20is%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20and%20is%20entitled%20to%20use%20its%20name%20and%20reserved%20symbol%20%26quot%3Bclock%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20the%20Election%20Symbols%20(Reservation%20and%20Allotment)%20Order%2C%201968%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Election%20Commission%20had%20said%20in%20its%20140-page%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20had%20said%20there%20were%20serious%20inconsistencies%20in%20terms%20of%20timelines%20in%20the%20claim%20of%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20group%20on%20organisational%20majority%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20unreliability%20of%20their%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20also%20expressed%20the%20hope%20that%20political%20parties%20will%20adopt%20good%20disclosure%20practices%20of%20organisational%20elections%20and%20internal%20party%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20assembly%20speaker%20on%20February%2015%2C%20the%20deadline%20fixed%20by%20the%20top%20court%20for%20deciding%20disqualification%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20speaker%2C%20in%20his%20elaborate%20decision%2C%20di