%2C%20I%20need%20to%20give%20my%20100%20per%20cent%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaiswal%20said%20after%20India%20took%20a%202-1%20lead%20in%20the%20five-match%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20trying.%20Whenever%20I'm%20set%2C%20I%20try%20to%20make%20it%20big.%20Because%20in%20Test%20cricket%20you%20never%20know%2C%20when%20you're%20playing%20well%20you%20have%20to%20make%20it%20big.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysing%20his%20double%20century%2C%20Jaiswal%20said%20he%20just%20tried%20to%20play%20session%20by%20session%20and%20also%20had%20to%20overcome%20a%20back%20problem%20en%20route%20the%20knock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20pretty%20difficult%20for%20me%20because%20initially%20I%20wasn't%20getting%20runs.%20So%20had%20to%20play%20the%20session%2C%20and%20get%20set.%20That's%20when%20I%20felt%20I%20could%20score%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20a%20while%20my%20back%20was%20not%20good.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20go%20out%20(of%20the%20field)%20but%20since%20it%20was%20too%20much%2C%20I%20went%20out.%20Today%20when%20I%20came%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20I%20take%20the%20game%20forward%20and%20bat%20till%20the%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20left-hander%20said%20as%20an%20opener%20his%20job%20is%20to%20give%20the%20team%20a%20good%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20there%20was%20something%20in%20the%20wicket%20and%20the%20ball%20was%20hard.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20is%20important%20for%20me%20to%20give%20teams%20a%20good%20start%20so%20it%20was%20important%20for%20me%20to%20play%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaiswal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20tell%20myself%20whenever%20I%20get%20set%2C%20I%20need%20to%20score%20well%20because%20you%20can%20get%20out%20anytime.%20My%20seniors%20have%20said%20to%20make%20it%20count.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20motivated%20by%20the%20knocks%20of%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3