rikes-in-houthi-controlled-areas-of-yemen-military-says%2Farticleshow%2F107800588.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-conducted-five-self-defense-strikes-in-houthi-controlled-areas-of-yemen-military-says%2Famp_articleshow%2F107800588.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-conducted-five-self-defense-strikes-in-houthi-controlled-areas-of-yemen-military-says%2Famp_articleshow%2F107800588.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPeople%20In%20Dressing%20Room%20Matter%20To%20Us%26quot%3B%3A%20Ben%20Stokes%20On%20'Bazball'%20Criticism%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20434-run%20loss%20against%20India%20on%20Sunday%20at%20Rajkot%2C%20England%20Test%20skipper%20Ben%20Stokes%20asserted%20that%20the%20team%20will%20look%20to%20win%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20two%20Tests%20at%20Ranchi%20and%20Dharamshala%20respectively%20to%20seal%20the%20series%203-2.%20A%20five-wicket%20haul%20by%20ace%20all-rounder%20and%20first-innings%20centurion%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20and%20top%20knocks%20from%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20double%20centurion%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20and%20debutant%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20saw%20England%20sink%20to%20its%20knees%20and%20surrender%20to%20the%20hosts%20inside%20four%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBen%20Duckett%20played%20an%20unbelievable%20innings.%20That%20was%20the%20tone%20we%20wanted%20to%20set%20throughout%20the%20innings.%20It%20was%20about%20identifying%20that%20opportunity%20and%20getting%20as%20close%20to%20India's%20total.%20We%20wanted%20to%20bowl%20yesterday%20but%20it%20was%20earlier%20than%20when%20we%20wanted.%20Sometimes%20game%20plans%20don't%20work%20and%20that%20was%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20Stokes%20said%20in%20the%20post-match%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone's%20got%20a%20perception%20and%20opinion%20about%20things%2C%20the%20people%20in%20the%20dressing%20room%20is%20what%20matters%20to%20us.%201-2%20down%20in%20the%20series%20and%20a%20great%20opportunity%20for%20us%20to%20come%20back%20and%20win%20the%20series.%20We%20leave%20this%20game%20behind%20and%20we%20know%20we%20have%20to%20win%20the%20next%202%20games%20to%20win%20the%20series%20and%20that's%20what%20we'll%20look%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2032-year-old%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20the%20Three%20Lions%20while%20chasing%20557%20was%20bundled%20out%20for%20just%20122%20runs%20in%2039.4%2C%20losing%20the%20match%20by%20434%20runs.%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20took%205%2F41%2C%20while%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20took%20two%20wickets.%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20and%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20took%20a%20wicket%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20India%20secured%20a%20556-run%20second%20innings%20lead%2C%20declaring%20their%20second%20innings%20at%20430%2F4.%20Following%20skipper%20Rohit's%20early%20fall%20for%20just%2019%20runs%2C%20young%20batters%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20and%20Shubman%20Gill%20steadied%20the%20ship%20for%20India%20with%20a%20155-run%20partnership%20for%20second%20wicket%2C%20which%20ended%20after%20Jaiswal%20retired%20hurt%20for%20104.%20India%20ended%20the%20day%20three%20at%20196%2F2%2C%20with%20Gill%20(65*)%20and%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20(3*).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20day%20four%2C%20Gill%20and%20Kuldeep%20continued%20to%20stitch%20yet%20another%20partnership%2C%20which%20ended%20with%20Gill%20heartbreakingly%20missing%20his%20fourth%20Test%20ton%20due%20to%20a%20run-out%2C%20scoring%2091%20in%20151%20balls%2C%20with%20nine%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes.%20Kuldeep%20also%20made%20a%20solid%2027%20in%2091%20balls%2C%20leaving%20India%20at%20258%2F4.%20From%20this%20point%20on%2C%20Jaiswal%20resumed%20his%20innings%20with%20fellow%20Mumbai%20star%20Sarfaraz%20Khan.%20Both%20took%20the%20English%20spinners%20to%20cleaners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal%20scored%20his%20second%20double-century%20in%20Tests%20after%20scoring%20his%20first%20one%20in%20the%20last%20Test.%20A%20key%20highlight%20of%20his%20knock%20was%20smashing%20veteran%20pace%20legend%20James%20Anderson%20for%20a%20hat-trick%20of%20sixes.%20Sarfaraz%20also%20scored%20his%20back-to-back%20half-century%20on%20Test%20debut.%20India%20ended%20the%20innings%20at%20430%2F4%2C%20with%20Jaiswal%20(214*%20in%20236%20balls%2C%2014%20fours%20and%2012%20sixes)%20and%20Sarfaraz%20(68*%20in%2072%20balls%2C%20with%20six%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes)%20unbeaten%20to%20form%20a%20172-run%20partnership%20for%20the%20fifth%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoe%20Root%2C%20Tom%20Hartley%20and%20Rehan%20Ahmed%20took%20a%20wicket%20each%20for%20England.Earlier%2C%20England%20in%20their%20first%20inning%20scored%20319%20runs%20in%20reply%20to%20India's%20445%20runs%20in%20their%20first%20inning.%20Though%20Ben%20Duckett%20(153%20in%20151%20balls%2C%20with%2023%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%20scored%20the%20fastest%20century%20by%20an%20English%20player%20in%20India%2C%20no%20other%20batter%20could%20give%20him%20much%20support.%20Skipper%20Stokes%20(41%20in%2089%20balls%2C%20with%20six%20fours)%20and%20Pope%20(39%20in%2055%20balls%2C%20with%20five%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20played%20some%20decent%20knocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiraj%20was%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20bowlers%20for%20India%20with%204%2F84%2C%20while%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20took%20two%20wickets%20each.%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20managed%20a%20scalp%20each%2C%20with%20the%20latter%20reaching%20his%20500th%20Test%20wicket%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20innings%2C%20after%20opting%20to%20bat%20first%2C%20India%20put%20up%20445%20in%20the%20first%20innings.%20The%20hosts%20were%20rocked%20by%20England%20bowlers%20earlier%20and%20were%20struggling%20at%2033%2F3.%20Then%20skipper%20Rohit%20stepped%20up%2C%20forming%20a%20204-run%20stand%20with%20Jadeja.%20Rohit%20scored%20131%20runs%20in%20196%20balls%2C%20with%2014%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes.%20Jadeja%20went%20on%20to%20score%20his%20third%20Test%20ton%20and%20crafted%20a%2077-run%20stand%20with%20debutant%20Sarfaraz%20(62%20in%2066%20balls%2C%20with%20nine%20fours%20and%20a%20six).%20Useful%20scores%20from%20debutant%20Dhruv%20Jurel%20(46%20in%20104%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes)%20and%20Ashwin%20(37%20in%2089%20balls%2C%20with%20six%20fours)%20took%20India%20to%20a%20fine%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMark%20Wood%20justified%20his%20selection%20with%20figures%20of%204%2F114.%20Rehan%20got%20two%20wickets%20while%20Root%2C%20Hartley%20and%20Anderson%20got%20a%20wicket%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJadeja%20was%20awarded%20the%20Player%20of%20the%20Match%20for%20his%20all-round%20performance%20in%20the%20Test%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708272780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Flftioia_ben-stokes-mark-wood-afp_625x300_18_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fpeople-in-dressing-room-matter-to-us-ben-stokes-on-bazball-criticism-after-rajkot-test-humbling-5082305%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Following%20a%20434-run%20loss%20against%20India%20on%20Sunday%20at%20Rajkot%2C%20the%20England%20team%20has%20come%20under%20harsh%20criticism%20from%20former%20players.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Boy%2C%208%2C%20Catches%20Life-Threatening%20Bug%20From%20Eating%20Eggs%20At%20Five-Star%20Resort%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20eight-year-old%2C%20Jaxon%20Bentley%2C%20boy%20%26quot%3Balmost%20died%26quot%3B%20after%20contracting%20salmonella%20from%20eggs%20he%20ate%20during%20a%20stay%20at%20a%20five-star%20resort%20in%20Turkey.%20His%20mother%2C%20Natalie%20Parr%2C%20stated%20that%20her%20son%20has%20been%20left%20%26quot%3Ba%20shell%20of%20what%20he%20used%20to%20be%26quot%3B%20after%20suffering%20kidney%20failure%20due%20to%20the%20bacteria%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2024%2F02%2F18%2Fboy-8-got-deadly-bug-eating-eggs-five-star-resort-20300848%2F%3Fico%3Dtop-stories_home_top%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMetro%20UK%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20was%20on%20a%20week-long%20holiday%20in%20June%20last%20year%20when%20he%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital%20with%20severe%20stomach%20cramps%2C%20diarrhoea%2C%20and%20a%20high%20temperature%20on%20the%20third%20day%20of%20the%20trip.%20He%20was%20able%20to%20fly%20back%20to%20the%20UK%20and%20was%20soon%20taken%20to%20a%20clinic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20later%20determined%20that%20two%20strains%20of%20salmonella%2C%20one%20of%20which%20can%20be%20deadly%20and%20cause%20neurological%20damage%2C%20were%20the%20cause%20of%20his%20symptoms.%20The%20boy%20was%20admitted%20and%20discharged%20from%20the%20hospital%20multiple%20times%20over%20several%20weeks.%20According%20to%20his%20mother%2C%20this%20traumatized%20him%20and%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20make%20complete%20recovery%20even%20six%20months%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJaxon%20is%20back%20at%20home%20and%20while%20we've%20tried%20to%20go%20back%20to%20a%20normal%20life%2C%20we're%20not%20there%20yet.%20He%20still%20cannot%20eat%20properly%20without%20pain.%20A%20once%20lively%2C%20outgoing%20boy%20went%20on%20holiday%20to%20Turkey%20came%20back%20a%20shell%20of%20what%20he%20used%20to%20be%20and%20the%20change%20is%20simply%20heart-breaking.%20My%20son%20has%20been%20replaced%20by%20a%20quiet%2C%20subdued%20boy%2C%20still%20traumatised%20by%20the%20experience%2C%20with%20night%20terrors%20meaning%20he's%20afraid%20to%20sleep%20as%20well%20as%20afraid%20to%20eat.%20The%20thought%20of%20any%20other%20family%20going%20through%20this%20is%20too%20much%20to%20think%20about%2C%20so%20we%20knew%20we%20had%20to%20speak%20out%20on%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20mother%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20can%20help%20prevent%20others%20going%20through%20the%20hell%20we%20are%20going%20through%2C%20that%20will%20be%20some%20comfort.%20For%20us%2C%20all%20we%20really%20want%20is%20the%20boy%20who%20went%20away%20on%20holiday%20to%20come%20back%20to%20us.%26quot%3B%20Her%20son%20was%20reliant%20on%20a%20wheelchair%20due%20to%20weakness%20and%20antibiotics%20failed%20to%20help%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20number%20of%20medical%20procedures%20were%20conducted%20%26quot%3Bincluding%20a%20lumbar%20puncture%20and%20two%20brain%20scans%20under%20general%20anaesthetic%26quot%3B.%20He%20was%20discharged%20again%20but%20was%20unable%20to%20gain%20weight%20and%20has%20been%20extremely%20weak.%20Regular%20blood%20tests%20are%20still%20being%20conducted%20to%20monitor%20his%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2036-year-old%20mother%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BWe'd%20all%20been%20looking%20forward%20so%20much%20to%20this%20holiday%20but%20due%20to%20Jaxon's%20illness%2C%20it's%20now%20one%20we'll%20remember%20forever%20for%20all%20the%20wrong%20reasons.%20He%20became%20so%20very%20ill%2C%20so%20quickly%2C%20that%20we%20knew%20it%20was%20more%20than%20just%20a%20typical%20upset%20stomach.%20It%20was%20frightening%20to%20have%20to%20see%20him%20in%20hospital%20and%20it%20was%20horrible%20to%20see%20what%20he%20was%20going%20through%20and%20see%20him%20becoming%20visibly%20weaker%20before%20our%20eyes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20knew%20we%20had%20to%20try%20to%20get%20him%20to%20a%20hospital%20at%20home%20if%20we%20possibly%20could%20and%20the%20flight%20home%20was%20the%20stuff%20of%20nightmares.%20He%20was%20so%20visibly%20ill%20and%20in%20pain%20that%20passengers%20on%20the%20plane%20cried%20seeing%20him%20in%20that%20condition.%20No%20one%20would%20believe%20someone%20could%20be%20so%20ill%20from%20a%20gastric%20illness%20or%20that%20the%20effects%20could%20be%20so%20serious.%20You%20feel%20so%20helpless%20when%20you%20can't%20do%20anything%20for%20your%20own%20child%20and%20I%20wish%20it%20could%20have%20been%20me%20instead%20of%20him%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708272360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F4b2all6_hospital_625x300_18_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-boy-8-catches-life-threatening-bug-from-eating-eggs-at-five-star-resort-5082562%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20family%20was%20on%20a%20week-long%20holiday%20in%20June%20last%20year%20when%20he%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20hospital%20with%20severe%20stomach%20cramps%2C%20diarrhoea%2C%20and%20a%20high%20temperature%20on%20the%20third%20day%20of%20the%20trip.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-boy-8-catches-life-threatening-bug-from-eating-eggs-at-five-star-resort-5082562%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-boy-8-catches-life-threatening-bug-from-eating-eggs-at-five-star-resort-5082562%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-boy-8-catches-life-threatening-bug-from-eating-eggs-at-five-star-resort-5082562%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kamal%20Nath's%20'Party%20Switch%20Suspense'%20Over%3F%20Congress%20Says%20He%20Is%20Staying%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20claimed%20that%20its%20veteran%20leader%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20is%20not%20joining%20the%20BJP.%20This%20is%20what%20Mr%20Nath%20has%20told%20them%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20matter%2C%20party%20general%20secretary%20Jitendra%20Singh%20told%20NDTV%20this%20evening.%20Mr%20Nath%20is%20in%20Delhi%20amid%20a%20buzz%20that%20he%20is%20joining%20the%20BJP%2C%20upset%20over%20his%20removal%20from%20the%20state%20party%20chief%20post%20after%20the%20Congress's%20crushing%20def