the%20work%20done.%20I%20will%20also%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20sources%20said%20party%20leaders%20including%20Jitu%20Patwari%2C%20were%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20MLAs%20to%20avert%20a%20mass%20exodus%20in%20case%20Mr%20Nath%20does%20change%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20those%20under%20spotlight%20include%20former%20ministers%20Sajjan%20Singh%20Verma%20and%20Sukhdev%20Panse%20and%20MLAs%20Satish%20Singh%20Sikarwar%2C%20Sukhdev%20Panse%2C%20Sanjay%20Uikey%2C%20Nilesh%20Uikey%2C%20Sohan%20Valmiki%2C%20Vijay%20Chaure%2C%20Kamlesh%20Shah%20and%20Lakhan%20Ghangoriya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20also%20said%20a%20section%20of%20BJP%20leaders%20had%20objected%20to%20Mr%20Nath's%20inclusion%20in%20the%20party%20on%20account%20of%20his%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%201984%20anti-Sikh%20riots.%20BJP%20leader%20Tajinder%20Pal%20Singh%20Bagga%20had%20raised%20questions%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20in%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20plan%20b%20where%20Mr%20Nath's%20son%20Nakul%20Nath%2C%20the%20MP%20from%20Chhindwara%2C%20joined%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20final%20call%20was%20expected%20to%20be%20taken%20in%20the%20matter%20by%20theb%20BJP%20hig%20command%2C%20sources%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708272360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fgvr2do48_kamal-nath_625x300_24_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkamal-nath-not-going-to-bjp-conveys-the-same-to-congress-leadership-amid-huge-buzz-on-switch-5082169%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20has%20claimed%20that%20its%20veteran%20leader%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20is%20not%20joining%20the%20BJP.%20This%20is%20what%20Mr%20Nath%20has%20told%20them%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20matter%2C%20party%20general%20secretary%20Jitendra%20Singh%20told%20NDTV%20this%20evening.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engage