se%2012%20who%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20seven%20are%20known%20PFI%20volunteers.%20So%20this%20is%20not%20just%20SFI%20what%20the%20government%20is%20doing.%20They%20are%20telling%20the%20members%20of%20a%20banned%20organisation%20that%20if%20you%20join%20these%20protests%2C%20you%20do%20something%20nasty%20and%20then%20we%20will%20protect%20you.%20This%20is%20an%20SFI%20and%20PFI%20joint%20venture.%20Seven%20of%20them%20belong%20to%20the%20PFI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20government%20is%20not%20only%20sheltering%20the%20PFI%20members%20of%20a%20banned%20organisation%20to%20create%20a%20law-and-order%20problem%20in%20Kerala.%20And%20I%20have%20already%20said%20that%20they%20are%20doing%20these%20things%20to%20provoke%20me%20to%20take%20some%20abstract%20action.%20But%20I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20oblige%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Kerala%20Governor%20Arif%20Mohammed%20Khan%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Students%20Federation%20of%20India%20(SFI)%20staged%20a%20black%20flag%20protest%20against%20the%20Governor%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESFI%2C%20a%20student%20wing%20of%20the%20ruling%20CPI(M)%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20Governor%20pushed%20%26quot%3BBJP-RSS%20nominees%26quot%3B%20into%20various%20universities%20in%20Kerala%2C%20using%20his%20authority%20as%20the%20chancellor%20of%20universities%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708269360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F3h3bhnug_arif-mohammed-khan_625x300_26_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-am-not-responding-to-criminals-kerala-governor-attacks-kerala-education-minister-5080930%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kerala%20Governor%20Arif%20Mohammed%20Khan%20slammed%20state%20higher%20education%20mi