2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwas-a-lack-of-ukrainian-ammunition-to-blame-for-russia-taking-avdiivka-13074914%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit's%20%26quot%3BYou%20Stay%20Calm%26quot%3B%20Dig%20At%20England's%20Bazball%20After%203rd%20Test%20Hammering%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20veiled%20dig%20at%20England%20over%20is%20'Bazball'%20style%20of%20cricket%20after%20India%20steam-rolled%20the%20visitors%20by%20a%20massive%20434%20runs%20in%20the%20third%20Test%20at%20Rajkot%2C%20with%20a%20day%20to%20spare%2C%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20said%20staying%20in%20the%20game%20for%20all%20five%20days%20was%20more%20important%20than%20winning%20in%20two%20or%20three%20days.%20A%20five-wicket%20haul%20by%20ace%20all-rounder%20and%20first-innings%20centurion%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20and%20top%20knocks%20from%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20double%20centurion%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20and%20debutant%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20saw%20England%20sink%20to%20its%20knees%20and%20surrender%20to%20the%20hosts%20inside%20four%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sparkling%20victory%20saw%20the%20hosts%20go%202-1%20up%20in%20the%20five-match%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20post-match%20presentation%2C%20Rohit%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20play%20Test%20cricket%2C%20you%20do%20not%20play%20it%20in%20two%20or%20three%20days.%20You%20have%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20game%20for%20five%20days.%20They%20played%20good%20shots%20(in%20the%20second%20innings)%20and%20put%20us%20under%20pressure%20but%20we%20have%20got%20class%20in%20our%20squad%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20bowling.%20So%20obviously%20the%20message%20was%20to%20stay%20calm%20(after%20day%20two).%20Important%20that%20time%20to%20stay%20calm%2C%20otherwise%20you%20drift.%20We%20stuck%20to%20our%20plans%20on%20day%20three%2C%20and%20when%20those%20things%20happen%2C%20it%20is%20a%20delight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Jadeja%20promoted%20to%20number%20five%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20and%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20notching%20up%20two%20half-centuries%20in%20his%20debut%20Test%2C%20the%20India%20skipper%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20this%20game%2C%20we%20thought%20he%20(Jadeja)%20has%20so%20much%20experience%20in%20this%20format%2C%20and%20scored%20lot%20of%20runs%20of%20late.%20We%20also%20wanted%20left-right%20batting%20as%20well.%20Sarfaraz%20being%20Sarfaraz%2C%20we%20know%20his%20quality%2C%20we%20wanted%20him%20to%20have%20some%20time%20before%20he%20comes%20out%20to%20bat.%20We%20saw%20what%20he%20can%20do%20with%20the%20bat.%20By%20no%20means%20is%20it%20some%20long%20plan%20with%20the%20batting%20order%2C%20we%20go%20with%20what%20is%20right%20for%20us%20for%20that%20Test%20match.%20Including%20calculating%20what%20the%20opponents'%20bowling%20attack%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20what%20he%20felt%20was%20the%20turning%20point%20of%20the%20match%2C%20Rohit%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLots%20of%20turning%20points.%20Once%20we%20won%20the%20toss%2C%20that%20was%20a%20good%20toss%20to%20win.%20We%20know%20runs%20on%20board%20is%20important%20in%20India.%20The%20lead%20was%20also%20crucial%20for%20us.%20The%20way%20we%20came%20out%20to%20bowl%20after%20the%20English%20batters'%20onslaught%2C%20important%20to%20stay%20calm...%20the%20bowlers%20showed%20a%20lot%20of%20character.%20Not%20to%20forget%20we%20did%20not%20have%20our%20most%20experienced%20bowler%20too%20(Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20who%20missed%20the%20day%20three%20due%20to%20personal%20reasons).%20I%20was%20proud%20to%20watch%20the%20bowlers.%20Then%20in%20our%20second%20innings%2C%20we%20knew%20half%20the%20job%20was%20done.%20We%20wanted%20to%20extend%20the%20lead%2C%20and%20the%20two%20youngsters%20helped%20extend.%20And%20then%20finally%20Jadeja.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELavishing%20praise%20on%20young%20opener%20Jaiswal%2C%20who%20is%20in%20the%20form%20of%20his%20life%20in%20the%20ongoing%20series%20and%20brought%20his%20second%20double%20ton%20in%20Tests%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20at%20Rajkot%2C%20Rohit%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20spoken%20a%20lot%20about%20him.%20I%20am%20sure%20people%20outside%20the%20changing%20room%20have%20also%20been%20talking%20about%20him.%20I%20want%20to%20be%20calm%20about%20him%2C%20not%20talk%20a%20lot%20about%20him.%20He%20has%20started%20his%20career%20on%20a%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChasing%20557%2C%20England%20was%20bundled%20out%20for%20just%20122%20runs%20in%2039.4%2C%20losing%20the%20match%20by%20434%20runs.%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20took%205%2F41%2C%20while%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20took%20two%20wickets.%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20and%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20took%20a%20wicket%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20India%20secured%20a%20556-run%20second%20innings%20lead%2C%20declaring%20their%20second%20innings%20at%20430%2F4.%20Following%20skipper%20Rohit's%20early%20fall%20for%20just%2019%20runs%2C%20young%20batters%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20and%20Shubman%20Gill%20steadied%20the%20ship%20for%20India%20with%20a%20155-run%20partnership%20for%20the%20second%20wicket%2C%20which%20ended%20after%20Jaiswal%20retired%20hurt%20for%20104.%20India%20ended%20the%20day%20three%20at%20196%2F2%2C%20with%20Gill%20(65*)%20and%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20(3*).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20day%20four%2C%20Gill%20and%20Kuldeep%20continued%20to%20stitch%20yet%20another%20partnership%2C%20which%20ended%20with%20Gill%20heartbreakingly%20missing%20his%20fourth%20Test%20ton%20due%20to%20a%20run-out%2C%20scoring%2091%20in%20151%20balls%2C%20with%20nine%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes.%20Kuldeep%20also%20made%20a%20solid%2027%20in%2091%20balls%2C%20leaving%20India%20at%20258%2F4.%20From%20this%20point%20on%2C%20Jaiswal%20resumed%20his%20innings%20with%20the%20fellow%20Mumbai%20star%20Sarfaraz%20Khan.%20Both%20took%20the%20English%20spinners%20to%20cleaners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal%20scored%20his%20second%20double-century%20in%20Tests%20after%20scoring%20his%20first%20one%20in%20the%20last%20Test.%20A%20key%20highlight%20of%20his%20knock%20was%20smashing%20veteran%20pace%20legend%20James%20Anderson%20for%20a%20hat-trick%20of%20sixes.%20Sarfaraz%20also%20scored%20his%20back-to-back%20half-century%20on%20Test%20debut.%20India%20ended%20the%20innings%20at%20430%2F4%2C%20with%20Jaiswal%20(214*%20in%20236%20balls%2C%2014%20fours%20and%2012%20sixes)%20and%20Sarfaraz%20(68*%20in%2072%20balls%2C%20with%20six%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes)%20unbeaten%20to%20form%20a%20172-run%20partnership%20for%20the%20fifth%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoe%20Root%2C%20Tom%20Hartley%20and%20Rehan%20Ahmed%20took%20a%20wicket%20each%20for%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20England%20in%20their%20first%20inning%20scored%20319%20runs%20in%20reply%20to%20India's%20445%20runs%20in%20their%20first%20inning.%20Though%20Ben%20Duckett%20(153%20in%20151%20balls%2C%20with%2023%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%20scored%20the%20fastest%20century%20by%20an%20English%20player%20in%20India%2C%20no%20other%20batter%20could%20give%20him%20much%20support.%20Skipper%20Stokes%20(41%20in%2089%20balls%2C%20with%20six%20fours)%20and%20Pope%20(39%20in%2055%20balls%2C%20with%20five%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20played%20some%20decent%20knocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiraj%20was%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20bowlers%20for%20India%20with%204%2F84%2C%20while%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20took%20two%20wickets%20each.%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20managed%20a%20scalp%20each%2C%20with%20the%20latter%20reaching%20his%20500th%20Test%20wicket%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20innings%2C%20after%20opting%20to%20bat%20first%2C%20India%20put%20up%20445%20in%20the%20first%20innings.%20The%20hosts%20were%20rocked%20by%20England%20bowlers%20earlier%20and%20were%20struggling%20at%2033%2F3.%20Then%20skipper%20Rohit%20stepped%20up%2C%20forming%20a%20204-run%20stand%20with%20Jadeja.%20Rohit%20scored%20131%20runs%20in%20196%20balls%2C%20with%2014%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes.%20Jadeja%20went%20on%20to%20score%20his%20third%20Test%20ton%20and%20crafted%20a%2077-run%20stand%20with%20debutant%20Sarfaraz%20(62%20in%2066%20balls%2C%20with%20nine%20fours%20and%20a%20six).%20Useful%20scores%20from%20debutant%20Dhruv%20Jurel%20(46%20in%20104%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes)%20and%20Ashwin%20(37%20in%2089%20balls%2C%20with%20six%20fours)%20took%20India%20to%20a%20fine%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMark%20Wood%20justified%20his%20selection%20with%20figures%20of%204%2F114.%20Rehan%20got%20two%20wickets%20while%20Root%2C%20Hartley%20and%20Anderson%20got%20a%20wicket%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJadeja%20took%20home%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20award%20for%20his%20century%20and%20seven%20wickets%20in%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708267320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F95sffhb_rohit-sharma-bcci_625x300_18_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Frohit-sharmas-you-stay-calm-dig-at-englands-bazball-after-rajkot-test-hammering-5081740%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20said%20staying%20in%20the%20game%20for%20all%20five%20days%20was%20more%20important%20than%20winning%20in%20two%20or%20three%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Vanga%20preserved%20Punjabi%20valour%20in%20Animal'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708267098000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107799657%2Cimgsize-75458.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsargun-mehta-and-gippy-grewal-laud-sandeep-reddy-vanga-for-depiction-of-sikhs-in-animal-he-kept-the-valour-of-punjabis-intact-t