20on%20Feb.%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20Feb.%2016%2C%202024%2C%20in%20penal%20colony%20number%203%2C%20convict%20Navalny%20A.A.%20felt%20unwell%20after%20a%20walk%2C%20almost%20immediately%20losing%20consciousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20medical%20staff%20of%20the%20institution%20arrived%20immediately%2C%20and%20an%20ambulance%20team%20was%20called.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20necessary%20resuscitation%20measures%20were%20carried%20out%2C%20which%20did%20not%20give%20positive%20results.%20Doctors%20of%20the%20ambulance%20stated%20the%20death%20of%20the%20convict.%20The%20causes%20of%20death%20are%20being%20established.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20more%20details%20about%20the%20death%20have%20been%20given%20by%20the%20penitentiary%20service%20or%20by%20medical%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Sudden%20Death%20Syndrome'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny's%20wife%20Yulia%2C%20speaking%20in%20Munich%20just%20a%20few%20hours%20after%20the%20announcement%2C%20said%20that%20she%20did%20not%20know%20whether%20or%20not%20to%20believe%20the%20news%20due%20to%20what%20she%20said%20were%20the%20lies%20of%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Navalny's%20spokeswoman%20Kira%20Yarmysh%2C%20confirmed%20that%20Navalny%20was%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%2069-year-old%20mother%2C%20Lyudmila%2C%20had%20been%20given%20a%20notice%20of%20the%20death%2C%20Yarmysh%20said.%20The%20time%20of%20death%20in%20that%20notice%20was%202%3A17%20p.m.%20local%20time%20(0917%20GMT)%20on%20Feb.%2016%2C%20Yarmysh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Alexei's%20lawyer%20and%20mother%20arrived%20at%20the%20colony%20this%20morning%2C%20they%20were%20told%20that%20the%20cause%20of%20Navalny's%20death%20was%20sudden%20death%20syndrome%2C%26quot%3B%20Ivan%20Zhdanov%2C%20who%20directs%20Navalny's%20Anti-Corruption%20Foundation%2C%20said%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSudden%20death%20syndrome%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20vague%20term%20for%20different%20cardiac%20syndromes%20that%20cause%20sudden%20cardiac%20arrest%20and%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20unidentified%20source%20told%20state-controlled%20RT%20that%20Navalny%20died%20from%20a%20blood%20clot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Body%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20unclear%20where%20Navalny's%20body%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20mother%20had%20been%20told%20that%20the%20body%20had%20been%20taken%20to%20Salekhard%2C%20the%20town%20near%20the%20prison%20complex%20but%20when%20she%20arrived%20at%20the%20morgue%20it%20was%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%20by%20Navalny's%20lawyer%2C%20the%20morgue%20said%20it%20did%20not%20have%20Navalny's%20body%2C%20Yarmysh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20they%20were%20told%20by%20officials%20that%20the%20body%20would%20not%20be%20handed%20over%20until%20the%20investigation%20was%20complete%2C%20though%20earlier%20they%20had%20been%20told%20that%20the%20investigation%20had%20discovered%20no%20traces%20of%20criminality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%20we%20don't%20have%20access%20to%20the%20body%20and%20we%20don't%20know%20for%20sure%20where%20it%20is%2C%20and%20we%20demand%20that%20the%20Russian%20authorities%20immediately%20give%20Alexei's%20body%20to%20his%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Yarmysh%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Reuters%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20employee%20at%20the%20morgue%20in%20Salekhard%20told%20Reuters%20that%20Navalny's%20body%20had%20not%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENovaya%20Gazeta%20cited%20unidentified%20sources%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20body%20had%20been%20taken%20to%20the%20morgue%20at%20the%20Salekhard%20District%20Clinical%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20said%20that%20the%20body%20showed%20signs%20of%20bruising%20consistent%20with%20some%20sort%20of%20seizure%20as%20well%20as%20traces%20of%20heart%20massage%20attempts.%20The%20newspaper%20said%20it%20was%20unclear%20why%20his%20heart%20stopped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20Russian%20media%20reported%20that%20a%20special%20team%20of%20investigators%20had%20arrived%20from%20Moscow.%20It%20is%20unclear%20when%20the%20post-mortem%20will%20take%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealth%20Issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20the%20day%20before%20his%20death%2C%20Navalny%20was%20shown%20joking%20in%20court%20via%20a%20video%20link%20to%20court.%20In%20mirth%2C%20he%20requested%20a%20judge%20use%20some%20of%20his%20vast%20salary%20to%20top%20up%20his%20own%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20online%20news%20outlet%20SOTA%20reported%20that%20the%20court%20session%20was%20convened%20after%20an%20%26quot%3Bargument%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20prison%20officer%20who%20tried%20to%20confiscate%20Navalny's%20pen.%20Navalny%20wrote%20later%20on%20Thursday%20that%20he%20had%20been%20given%2015%20days%20in%20solitary%20confinement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussian%20prisons%20are%20brutal%20and%20his%20team%20had%20repeatedly%20raised%20fears%20that%20he%20would%20be%20harmed%20or%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20repeatedly%20placed%20in%20punishment%20cells%20for%20various%20offences%2C%20including%20for%20his%20attitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20joked%20about%20the%20conditions%2C%20the%20Polar%20Wolf%20colony%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20toughest%20prisons%20in%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20not%20been%20colder%20than%20-32C%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20Navalny%20said%20in%20January.%20%26quot%3BNothing%20quite%20invigorates%20you%20like%20a%20walk%20in%20Yamal%20at%206%3A30%20in%20the%20morning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20at%20this%20temperature%2C%20you%20can%20walk%20for%20more%20than%20half%20an%20hour%20only%20if%20you%20manage%20to%20grow%20a%20new%20nose%2C%20new%20ears%20and%20new%20fingers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20posted%20a%20picture%20of%20his%20walking%20yard%20-%20concrete-walled%2C%20topped%20with%20metal%20bars%2C%2011%20steps%20long%20and%20three%20steps%20wide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavalny%20mentioned%20a%20scene%20in%20the%202015%20film%20%26quot%3BThe%20Revenant%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20which%20Leonardo%20DiCaprio%20shelters%20in%20the%20carcass%20of%20a%20horse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20that%20would%20have%20worked%20here.%20A%20dead%20horse%20would%20freeze%20in%2015%20minutes%2C%26quot%3B%20Navalny%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20an%20elephant%20here%2C%20a%20hot%20elephant%2C%20a%20fried%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20he%20raised%20a%20little%20publicised%20problem%20that%20haunts%20Russia's%20prisons%3A%20a%20lack%20of%20teeth%20due%20to%20poor%20nutrition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20his%20team%20said%20he%20was%20grappling%20with%20severe%20stomach%20pain%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708266360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F9mdi1bh_alexei-navalny-reuters_625x300_17_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fputin-critic-alexei-navalny-found-died-in-arctic-prison-what-do-we-know-about-his-death-5082122%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alexei%20Navalny%2C%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20most%20prominent%20domestic%20foe%2C%20died%20on%20Friday%20at%20the%20Arctic%20prison%20where%20he%20was%20serving%20a%20three-decade%20prison%20term.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fputin-critic-alexei-navalny-found-died-in-arctic-prison-what-do-we-know-about-his-death-5082122%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fputin-critic-alexei-navalny-found-died-in-arctic-