Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%20(UAPA)%20case%20for%20allegedly%20making%20inflammatory%20speeches%20at%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20against%20a%20controversial%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20finding%20no%20direct%20incitement%20to%20violence%20or%20murder%20in%20his%20speeches%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20the%20court%20claimed%20that%20his%20rhetoric%20had%20a%20significant%20mobilising%20effect%20and%20potentially%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20outbreak%20of%20the%20February%202020%20riots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImam%20was%20arrested%20in%20January%202020%20and%20applied%20first%20for%20bail%20in%20July%202022.%20His%20lawyers%20argued%20that%20the%20since%20he%20had%20already%20spent%20four%20years%20in%20jail%20out%20of%20the%20maximum%20sentence%20of%20seven%20years%2C%20he%20was%20eligible%20for%20statutory%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fsharjeel-imam-not-ask-anyone-pick-weapons-speeches-captured-people-imagination-incited-delhi-court%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Imam%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20contended%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20suspended%20the%20offence%20of%20sedition%2C%20and%20the%20UAPA%20provisions%20applied%20in%20his%20case%20do%20not%20entail%20a%20sentence%20exceeding%20seven%20years.%20However%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20argued%20that%20the%20punishment%20for%20the%20offences%20invoked%20against%20him%20should%20be%20considered%20cumulatively%20rather%20than%20concurrently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20court%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20followed%20an%20order%20from%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20instructing%20it%20to%20expedite%20the%20decision%20on%20his%20bail%20plea.%20Imam%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20against%20the%20framing%20of%20charges%20is%20set%20for%20a%20hearing%20at%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20on%20March%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Additional%20Sess