20any%20role%20in%20enabling%20ship%20to%20carry%20armaments%20which%20may%20aggravate%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%20and%20particularly%20in%20Rafah%2C%20they%20have%20said%20%E2%80%9Cour%20Union%20members%20have%20collectively%20decided%20to%20refuse%20handling%20all%20types%20of%20weaponised%20cargoes.%20Loading%20and%20unloading%20these%20weapons%20helps%20provide%20organizations%20with%20the%20ability%20to%20kill%20innocent%20people.%E2%80%9D%20The%20trade%20union%20has%20also%20called%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20press%20release%20further%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9Cas%20responsible%20trade%20unions%2C%20we%20declare%20our%20solidarity%20with%20those%20who%20campaign%20for%20peace.%20We%20call%20upon%20the%20workers%20of%20the%20world%20and%20peace-loving%20people%20to%20stand%20with%20the%20demand%20of%20free%20Palestine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20455px)%2085vw%2C%20455px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18155705%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-18-at-2.40.37-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22455%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18155705%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-18-at-2.40.37-PM.jpeg%20828w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18155705%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-18-at-2.40.37-PM-216x300.jpeg%20216w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F18155705%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-18-at-2.40.37-PM-738x1024.jpeg%20738w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-697717%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22631%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20Chennai%2C%20T.%20Narendra%20Rao%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Water%20Transport%20Federation%20of%20India%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20affiliated%20to%20the%20World%20Federation%20of%20Trade%20Unions%2C%20a%20global%20body.%20At%20a%20recent%20meeting%20of%20world%20trade%20unions%2C%20held%20at%20Athens%20after%20the%20war%20of%20Gaza%20started%2C%20we%20saw%20the%20rousing%20reception%20the%20trade%20union%20representative%20from%20Palestine%20got%20there%2C%20as%20they%20explained%20exactly%20what%20was%20going%20on.%20We%20decided%20them%20that%20we%20would%20do%20our%20bit%20and%20not%20handle%20any%20weapon-laden%20cargo%2C%20which%20will%20go%20onto%20assist%20Israel%20to%20kill%20more%20women%20and%20children%20as%20we%20are%20seeing%20and%20reading%20every%20day%20in%20the%20news.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERao%20said%20they%20had%20not%20encountered%20any%20reports%20of%20any%20such%20ship%20bound%20for%20Israel%20so%20far%2C%20but%20were%20issuing%20the%20statement%20%E2%80%9Cto%20express%20solidarity%20with%20Palestine%E2%80%9D%20and%20make%20clear%20that%20they%20would%20not%20be%20a%20part%20of%20any%20future%20enterprise%20to%20support%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20war%20on%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20Their%20workers%20%E2%80%9Cwould%20not%20help%20load%20or%20unload%20anything%20that%20advances%20the%20cause%20of%20war%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20Hyderabad-based%20joint%20venture%20in%20which%20the%20Adani%20Group%20has%20a%20controlling%20stake%20has%20manufactured%20and%20dispatched%20over%2020%20military%20drones%20to%20the%20Israeli%20military.%20Hermes%20drones%20%E2%80%93%20similar%20to%20what%20Adani-Elbit%20Advanced%20Systems%20India%20Ltd%20has%20just%20delivered%20%E2%80%93%20are%20being%20extensively%20used%20in%20the%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces%E2%80%99%20military%20campaign%20in%20Gaza%2C%20which%20have%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20over%2028%2C000%20people%2C%20including%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sale%20more%20of%20than%2020%20Hermes%20900%20medium-altitude%2C%20long-endurance%20(MALE)%20UAVs%20to%20Israel%20%E2%80%93%20first%20reported%20on%20February%202%20by%20Neelam%20Mathews%20for%20the%20well-regarded%20defence-related%20website%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shephardmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fuv-online%2Findia-sends-newly-assembled-male-uavs-to-israel%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EShephard%20Media%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0has%20not%20yet%20been%20publicly%20acknowledged%20by%20either%20Tel%20Aviv%20or%20New%20Delhi%20but%20sources%20at%20Adani%2C%20communicating%20off%20the%20record%20as%20they%20are%20not%20authorised%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20media%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-jv-just-exported-lethal-drones-to-israel-same-model-being-used-in-genocide-tainted-gaza-war%5C%22%3Ehad%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20early%20February%20that%20the%20export%20had%20indeed%20taken%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETh%20World%20Federation%20of%20Trade%20Unions%2C%20established%20in%201945%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wftucentral.org%2Fthe-wftu-on-the-forthcoming-attack-on-rafah-palestine%2F%5C%22%3Eon%20February%2013%20issued%20a%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20solidarity%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Palestine%2C%20saying%20that%20their%20demand%20was%20for%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20United%20Nations%20and%20the%20international%20community%20will%20take%20urgent%20decisions%20to%20prevent%20this%20new%20Nakba%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20land.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20condemn%20the%20hypocrisy%20of%20the%20USA%20and%20their%20allies%2C%20who%20pretend%20to%20be%20the%20protectors%20of%20the%20international%20law%20and%20order%2C%20but%20they%20silently%20or%20openly%20support%20this%20genocide.%E2%80%9D%20They%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20class-oriented%20trade%20union%20movement%2C%20once%20again%20expresses%20its%20unwavering%20solidarity%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20and%20reaffirms%20the%20readiness%20to%20intensify%20its%20actions%20in%20every%20possible%20means%2C%20until%20the%20end%20of%20the%20occupation%20and%20the%20liberation%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20land.%E2