20wanted%20something%20to%20shop%20for.%20So%2C%20I%20would%20visit%20the%20jewellery%20section%20because%20the%20items%20on%20sale%20there%20did%20not%20come%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20size%20limitations%20you%20see%20in%20apparel%20wear.%20In%20fact%2C%20on%20one%20of%20my%20posts%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20had%20people%20writing%20comments%20like%20%E2%80%98Went%20shopping%20for%20clothes%20but%20came%20back%20with%20a%20scrunchie%E2%80%99.%20Over%20time%2C%20I%20became%20a%20jewellery%20junkie%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20venture%20into%20the%20accessories%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAmid%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298376%2Fmolbio-diagnostics-truenat-covid-testing-raises-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5BCOVID-19%5D%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20was%20back%20home%20thinking%20about%20what%20to%20do%20next%20with%20my%20life.%20What%20I%20found%20was%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20affordable%20accessories%20segment%20and%20measured%20all%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20associated%20with%20running%20such%20a%20business.%20Eventually%2C%20I%20established%20%E2%80%98A%20Little%20Extra%E2%80%99%20in%20August%202020%20with%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%205%2C000%2C%20and%20here%20we%20are%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FDiksha-Singhi--1708004699.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Little%20Extra%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FDiksha-Singhi--1708004699.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FDiksha-Singhi--1708004699-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FDiksha-Singhi--1708004699-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FDiksha-Singhi--1708004699-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FDiksha-Singhi--1708004699-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341967%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20Little%20Extra%3A%20Diksha%20Singhi%20has%20built%20a%20women-led%20business.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98A%20Little%20Extra%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20jewellery%20made%20at%20%E2%80%98A%20Little%20Extra%E2%80%99%20has%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdistinctive%20element%E2%80%9D%20to%20it%2C%20according%20to%20Diksha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20buy%20conventional%20jewellery%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20either%20stone-based%20or%20they%20have%20a%20certain%20design%20or%20aesthetic.%20We%20wanted%20to%20make%20jewellery%20specific%20for%20an%20occasion%2C%20emotion%20or%20lifestyle.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20Navratri%2C%20what%20better%20than%20to%20wear%20our%20%E2%80%98Durga%20earrings%E2%80%99%20that%20are%20colourful%2C%20bright%20and%20have%20the%20chunkiest%20elements%20of%20shell%2C%20mirror%2C%20beads%2C%20etc%3F%20If%20you%20want%20to%20watch%20a%20football%20match%20in%20a%20stadium%2C%20cheering%20for%20your%20favourite%20team%2C%20why%20just%20wear%20those%20regular%20earrings%3F%20Why%20not%20wear%20earrings%20shaped%20and%20designed%20like%20a%20football%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20600px)%20100vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FA-Little-Extra-Durga-Earrings-1708004385.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Little%20Extra%20by%20Diksha%20Singhi%20just%20won%20Rs%2060%20lakh%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FA-Little-Extra-Durga-Earrings-1708004385.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FA-Little-Extra-Durga-Earrings-1708004385-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FA-Little-Extra-Durga-Earrings-1708004385-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FA-Little-Extra-Durga-Earrings-1708004385-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FA-Little-Extra-Durga-Earrings-1708004385-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341964%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDurga%20Earrings%20made%20by%20%E2%80%98A%20Little%20Extra%E2%80%99.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20create%20a%20certain%20emotional%20angle%20with%20the%20jewellery%20that%20you%E2%80%99re%20buying.%20Given%20the%20kind%20of%20occasion%2Femotion-specific%20earrings%20or%20the%20neck%20pieces%20we%20design%2C%20it%20also%20becomes%20easier%20to%20give%20the%20kind%20of%20accessories%20we%20make%20to%20other%20people%20as%20gifts.%20But%20we%20are%20also%20aware%20of%20a%20market%20which%20is%20looking%20for%20accessories%20with%20a%20minimal%20aesthetic%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20we%20also%20make%20jewellery%20with%20minimal%2Fsimple%20designs%20but%20with%20an%20extra%20touch%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20they%20have%20this%20limited%20collection%20of%20very%20small%20gold-plated%20brass%20earrings%20designed%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20a%20dragon.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20inspired%20by%20a%20very%20energetic%20and%20inspiring%20petite%20friend%20who%20was%20either%20bullied%20for%20being%20small%20in%20stature%20or%20not%20taken%20seriously%20as%20a%20result.%20Despite%20people%20counting%20her%20out%2C%20her%20energy%20has%20remained%20undiminished%20like%20a%20dragon.%20We%20also%20employ%20different%20handmade%20art%20forms%20like%C2%A0%3Cem%3EKada%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20beadwork%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EKundan%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ebrass%2C%20terracotta%2C%20cane%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20they%20make%20these%20accessories%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Little%20Extra%20works%20with%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ekarigars%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(artisans)%20specialising%20in%20different%20handmade%20art%20forms.%20Since%20the%20venture%20deals%20in%20various%20art%20forms%2C%20Diksha%20argues%20that%20she%20can%E2%80%99t%20have%20something%20in-house%20for%20production%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20our%3Cem%3E%C2%A0karigars%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0move%20their%20hands%20is%20something%20you%20and%20I%20cannot%20do.%20They%E2%80%99re%20skilled%20and%20work%20best%20when%20they%E2%80%99re%20in%20their%20community.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20pick%20them%20out%20of%20a%20village%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20bring%20them%20to%20Delhi%2C%20and%20expect%20them%20to%20do%20quality%20work.%20They%20would%20not%20be%20happy.%20They%20want%20to%20stay%20with%20their%20families.%20So%20our%20idea%20was%20to%20have%20these%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ekarigars%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0work%20in%20their%20own%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20present%20them%20with%20whatever%20designs%20we%20have%20come%20up%20with%20here.%20We%20send%20the%20designs%20across%20to%20our%20manager%20stationed%20with%20these%20artisan%20communities%20who%20then%20sits%20with%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ekarigars%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20develops%20those%20designs.%20Following%20this%2C%20they%20send%20us%20items%20for%20sampling%2C%20which%20we%20assess%20and%20see%20if%20there%20are%20any%20changes%20we%20would%20like%20on%20them.%20They%20eventually%20send%20us%20further%20samples%20which%20we%20approve%20and%20send%20for%20production.%20We%20follow%20this%20process%20for%20all%20our%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20terracotta%2C%20Diksha%E2%80%99s%20team%20works%20with%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ekarigars%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Efrom%20Assam%20and%20West%20Bengal.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20beadwork%2C%20they%20work%20with%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ekarigars%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0from%20Delhi-NCR%20states.%20If%20they%E2%80%99re%20employing%C2%A0%3Cem%3EKundan%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(a%20traditional%20form%20of%20gemstone%20jewellery)%2C%20they%20work%20with%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ekarigars%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0from%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mantra%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20working%20with%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ekarigars%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20to%20pay%20them%20what%20they%20ask%20for.%20Throughout%20my%20journey%2C%20I%20have%20seen%20people%20in%20my%20industry%20try%20to%20exploit%20them.%20My%20approach%20has%20always%20been%20the%20more%20they%20grow%2C%20the%20more%20we%20grow.%20Successfully%20selling%20over%2080%2C000%20products%20and%20developing%20a%20range%20of%20accessories%20with%20over%20500%20designs%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20grown%20together.%20Today%2C%20%E2%80%98A%20Little%20Extra%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20women-led%20enterprise%2C%20and%20I%20currently%20have%20eight%20full-time%20women%20employees%20with%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC23qIkXJUxz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC23qIkXJUxz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%