%20most%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318930%2Fhomestays-in-srinagar-kashmir-scenic-views-of-dal-lake-mughal-tulip-gardens-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eiconic%20adventures%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20have%20had%20together.%20The%20most%20wonderful%20part%2C%20according%20to%20them%2C%20was%20inking%20friendships%20with%20the%20local%20artisans%20of%20Sawantwadi%20who%20were%20delighted%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20recall%20the%20legacy%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Eganjifa%3C%2Fem%3E%20art%20you%20were%20treated%20to%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20tale%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20thrilled%20to%20know%20that%20the%20art%20finds%20its%20purest%20expression%20in%20the%20palace%20hotel%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20facades%2C%20the%20decor%2C%20the%20cutlery%2C%20the%20furnishings%2C%20and%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20warm%20welcome%20into%20the%20palace%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20astounding%20how%20much%20the%20Sawantwadi%20Palace%20relies%20on%20the%20bounty%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341177%2Fchhotaram-prajapat-mud-homestay-in-salawas-village-jodhpur-rajasthan-dhurrie-making%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evillage%E2%80%99s%20heritage%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20culture.%20Right%20from%20the%20cultural%20workshops%20that%20let%20tourists%20experiment%20with%20the%20%3Cem%3Eganjifa%3C%2Fem%3E%20art%20to%20the%20furnishings%20of%20the%20palace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20it%20has%20been%20preserved%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shraddha%2C%20elaborating%20on%20the%20furniture%20and%20the%20foundational%20structure.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20we%20had%20to%20strengthen%20some%20of%20the%20walls%20by%20installing%20metal%20planks%20especially%20since%20there%20is%20an%20influx%20of%20people%20now.%20We%20need%